f=AI & Agents/meta/custom/skill-authoring-standards/SKILL.md · in=house standard what goes INSIDE SKILL.md fleet. Pairs verbatim marketplace copy `writing-skills` (obra/superpowers): skill supplies test-driven authoring METHOD; one supplies format LAW. they conflict, skill wins. · p=Skills fleet's entire substance plain-text files. their format drifts, provenance vanishes, descriptions stop triggering, self-annealing loop nothing reliable edit. skill makes skill file auditable, discoverable, portable. · wu=Any new skill authored, adopted marketplace, merged., anneal prepares skill edit proposal (the edited file still comply)., audit flags frontmatter, naming, hardcoding violations. · st:/ Protocol=AUTHOR (or ADOPT) LINT (checklist below) TEST (writing-skills method) PROPOSE (Rail board) REGISTER (fleet-registry). · in=**1. Frontmatter required skill, exceptions:** **2. Body custom skills:** Introduction, Purpose, Use, Structure/Protocol, Instructions, Output Format, Principles, Fallback, Boundaries Skills. Marketplace copies keep source's structure, uncut, behind selection-rationale comment block. **3. Description discipline** (per Anthropic guidance writing-skills SDO): third person; triggering conditions, workflow summary; concrete symptoms keywords; under ~500 chars. **4. Conciseness:** body under 500 lines; heavy reference reusable scripts `assets/` `scripts/`, referenced one level deep only. **5. Genericization:** venture/product/stack names executable content; stack-specific material becomes DATED asset activated operator's stack/venture profile names it; unknown values `<FILL_IN>`, never invented. **6. Time-sensitivity:** anything stale (platform mechanics, tool versions, landscapes) lives dated asset re-verify note, never timeless method body. **7. Scripts:** justified constants, explicit error handling, tested sample input before skill presented done. · of=Authoring lint verdict: PASS numbered violations, citing rule number above. Machine check available: anneal's `skill_audit.py` covers rules mechanically; rest meta's judgment. · pr=provenance, skill unsourced skill file rumor., description API: doesn't trigger, skill doesn't exist., Format compliance never waived content quality ("it's good, ship it" drift kills fleet). · f=Source material another language translate fully before adoption (playbook 4.5). skill can't meet standard (e.g., identifiable source) rebuilt custom-from-scratch honest frontmatter, rejected. · b:with Other Skills=`writing-skills` (marketplace, agent): testing method REQUIRED BACKGROUND authoring; house format wins conflicts., agent-architecture-standards: everything outside SKILL.md file., anneal's skill-quality-audit: mechanical enforcement rules fleet scale., Shared `verification-before-completion`: binds author before declaring any skill done.